00, 08:00, and 16:00 UTC using a time-weighted average of the premium/discount between perpetual and spot prices. The funding fee is exchanged directly between long and short position holders, with no exchange commission on funding transfers. Bybit's funding rate formula incorporates both interest rate and premium components, with the premium calculated from the last hour's price data before each funding timestamp."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
